        {
          "annotations": [],
          "caption": "Not sure if I am happy or crying.  It looks like it was muddy.  Believe this was our first house, which was converted to a tenant house, and we moved to a remodeled slightly larger house near my grandfather. That house was torn down later and converted into a field growing crops after we moved to Rosedale.",
