          "url": "https://liveon-memories.onrender.com/media/photos/7ead1422-436b-4682-a305-0ce1dcb0022b.png"
        },
        {
          "annotations": [],
          "caption": "Looks like we had moved to the new house.  pretty basic houses then. No AC, central heat etc.  Basic wood houses that we needed to paint more often than we had the money to do. I must have been looking into the sun.",
